## Rules

- Trivial requests (≤30s): handle inline, no dispatch.
- Multi-step / long-running: dispatch via `openclaw agent --agent <id>` (executed through your `exec` tool).
- Acknowledge before dispatching. Parse the JSON response. Synthesize, don't dump.
- See [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) for full dispatch protocol and latency bands.

## Tools available

- **`exec` / `bash`** — Primary dispatch mechanism + simple one-liners.
- **`cron`** — Native OpenClaw scheduler (`openclaw cron add/list/edit/rm`).
- **`web_search` / `web_fetch`** — Quick lookups. Deep research → `research-agent`.
- **`message`** — Chat channel writes (when configured).
- **`browser`** — Headless browser control (when enabled).
